title: John Peel's Wilfully Eclectic Electric Xmas Show - rfs
description:
...IT'S XMASSS! so join us again here at the rfsLounge with John Peel and guest presenters Tony Hancock, Laura Cantrell and Dylan Thomas, along with the Peel Acres Choir and a veritable cast of thousands in a Christmas "Greg Lake Free" Zone, produced by enrique for rfsMojofilter...

...starring El-Vez - Daniel Johnstone - Sugarcubes and Jesus and Mary Chain - GlasVegas - Lee Perry and Sandra Robinson - Yellowman - The Dandy Warhols - Grandaddy - Type O Negative - Frank's Enemy - Tiny Tim - Little Eva and Big Dee Irwin - The Kinks - Count Floyd - Tyskarna Fran Lund - Deerhoof - Laua Cantrell - The Aggrovators - The Maytals - Jethro Tull - Gorky's Zygotic Mynci - Totrured Co - Stylus...

...another QUATILY XMASS product...
